#First to initialize using below command. 
#It looks for configuration files in current working directory and examines them if they need any provider plugings. 
#If yes, then it tries to download plugins from Public registry unless if specifying a location.

terraform init


#To generate plan use below command. It looks into current configuration & context of state data.
#Determines difference between two and makes a plan to update target environment to match desired configuration.
#It will print plan to look out and verify changes.

terraform plan

#To make available of desired configuration use below command. It runs above command and make changes to file. 
#Execute changes or modify target environment & state data will be updated to reflect changes.

terraform apply

#If we are done with our practice or use and to destroy all the desired configuration use below command. Be cautious while using this in production.

terraform destroy
